Options.Description:
Enables the following things on the hair:
- Glow (emissive) ;
- Iridescence ;
- [BETA] Perma-wetness ;
- [BETA] Metallic finish.

Enables the following things on character-related glass (eyeglasses and some gear, minions, mounts and ornaments):
- Iridescence ;
- [BETA] Perma-wetness.

Enables the following things on other character-related elements (gear, minions, mounts and ornaments):
- Iridescence ;
- [BETA] Perma-wetness ;
- Reactive glow ;
- Opacity remapping.
